social_posts.post_text: Avatar: the way of water premiere felt more like a family reunion. A wild creative process that was so crazy and fun with the people you love. Can’t wait for everyone to see this incredible experience 😭❤️ #avatarthewayofwater

This is one of my favorite moments in my stunt career. Working on the avatar sequels was surreal. Thank you @jamescameronofficial and @jonplandau for allowing me to be part of the entire process. And my biggest thanks goes to @garrettxwarren for always trusting me and allowing me to be part of everything and ultimately bringing me on this and many other projects. I love this video from @indiewire  so much about what we did for the action design for @avatar and the appreciation Jim and Jon shared to us all. I hope you all enjoy it as much as we do💙 #avatar #avatarthewayofwater #stuntman #film
Watch out…
Dear @jimmychhiu , I like fighting you. Sincerely, steve

#ad For last night’s #Oscars, @volvocarusa and @abcnetwork partnered to celebrate the talented professionals who work behind the scenes to help keep everyone safe on set—and make the movies we love possible. I was honored to be one of the people featured in the spot!
We made this up in a day for fun and never decided what “it” is they are looking for. So help us finish our little story with a comment below 🤣 #whatisit #stunts
